        "content": "AI LEAD ENRICHMENT & QUALIFICATION SYSTEM\n\nFeatures:\n• Lead capture\n• Company enrichment\n• AI lead scoring\n• Hot/warm/cold classification\n• Personalized outreach\n• CRM storage",
